## This was CS50!

Our final program brings everything together:

```py
import cowsay
import pyttsx3

engine = pyttsx3.init()
this = input("What's this? ")
cowsay.cow(this)
engine.say(this)
engine.runAndWait()
```

Running this program provides a spirited send-off—a cow speaks your words aloud.

Our great hope is that you will use what you learned in this course to address real problems in the world, making our globe a better place.

**This was CS50!**

